.services
  h2 MY WHEELHOUSE
  .services-wrap
    .service.active data-index='1'
      img.service-icon src='src/img/icon-service-web-development.svg' alt='Web Development'
      h3.service-title WEB DEVELOPMENT
      p.service-text I use research, inspiration, and the latest tools to construct an elegant final product. I build fast, responsive, efficient websites - always with great design in mind.
    .service data-index='2'
      img.service-icon src='src/img/icon-service-responsive-design.svg' alt='Responsive Design'
      h3.service-title RESPONSIVE DESIGN
      p.service-text Forget pre-packaged templates, grids, or frameworks. When I build websites they're made custom, flow perfectly to fit any device size, and are optimized for mobile users.
    .service data-index='3'
      img.service-icon src='src/img/icon-service-ios-apps.svg' alt='iOS App Development'
      h3.service-title iOS APP DEVELOPMENT
      p.service-text Bring your app idea to the iPhone and iPad. I design and code alongside Apple's guidelines to give your custom application the natural, native feel it deserves.
    .service data-index='4'
      img.service-icon src='src/img/icon-service-bespoke-interfaces.svg' alt='Bespoke Interfaces'
      h3.service-title BESPOKE INTERFACES
      p.service-text Data-driven websites and applications are no problem. Whether tapping into a third party API or constructing a back-end interface from scratch, I build to suit.

